27
00:01:10,604 --> 00:01:12,404
              NICE JAM SESSION. 

28
00:01:12,406 --> 00:01:15,340
    DON'T FORGET                
   THE BEST PART.               

29
00:01:15,342 --> 00:01:17,876
      [ SEAGULLS CALLING ]      
UH...                           

30
00:01:17,878 --> 00:01:20,112
      [ SEAGULLS SCREECH ]      
 [ SHOUTS ]                     

31
00:01:20,114 --> 00:01:21,780
                    HYAH!       

32
00:01:21,782 --> 00:01:23,348
                 HYAH! HYAH!    

33
00:01:23,350 --> 00:01:24,917
       RUN BACK TO YOUR MASTERS!

34
00:01:24,919 --> 00:01:28,921
      TELL THEM WE'RE NOT AFRAID
                OF YOUR KIND!   

35
00:01:28,923 --> 00:01:30,956
     [ LAUGHS ]                 
THANKS FOR SAVING MY JAM SNACK. 

36
00:01:30,958 --> 00:01:34,059
UNFORTUNATELY, IT'S NOT SAFE    
 FROM ME. [ MUNCH! ]            

37
00:01:34,061 --> 00:01:36,028
[ Muffled ] YOU'RE SUCH         
A GOOD SWORD FIGHTER, CONNIE.   

38
00:01:36,030 --> 00:01:38,597
             REALLY? I WAS JUST 
     SWINGING THIS THING AROUND.

39
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:40,566
             I DON'T REALLY KNOW
               WHAT I'M DOING.  

40
00:01:40,568 --> 00:01:44,269
           BUT I'D LOVE TO LEARN
