     YOU WANT ME TO DO WHAT?    

43
00:01:48,776 --> 00:01:50,375
         YOU SHOULD TRAIN CONNIE
               TO SWORD FIGHT.  

44
00:01:50,377 --> 00:01:52,111
          SHE'S ALREADY SO GOOD.
STEVEN!                         

45
00:01:52,113 --> 00:01:55,481
  BUT YOU ARE. Y-YOU HELPED ME  
  FIGHT THE ROBOT FLOATY THING, 

46
00:01:55,483 --> 00:01:57,583
   SHE TOOK DOWN THAT EVIL CLONE
                 OF HERSELF,    

47
00:01:57,585 --> 00:02:00,752
        UH...THOSE MEAN SEAGULLS
                  JUST NOW.     

48
00:02:00,754 --> 00:02:03,489
YOU'RE AWFULLY YOUNG            
TO BEGIN SOMETHING LIKE THIS.   

49
00:02:03,491 --> 00:02:06,725
BUT I SUPPOSE I WAS ONLY        
A FEW THOUSAND YEARS OLD        

50
00:02:06,727 --> 00:02:09,895
WHEN I BEGIN FIGHTING           
ALONGSIDE ROSE QUARTZ.          

51
00:02:09,897 --> 00:02:11,230
    YES, CONNIE?                

52
00:02:11,232 --> 00:02:13,298
    PLEASE, I WANT TO LEARN.    

53
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:15,934
      I MEAN, I DON'T KNOW      
 WHAT WILL HAPPEN IN THE FUTURE.

54
00:02:15,936 --> 00:02:18,470
   BUT IF SOMETHING DANGEROUS   
          COMES ALONG,          

55
00:02:18,472 --> 00:02:20,806
  I DON'T WANT TO BE A BURDEN.  
         I WANT TO HELP!        

56
00:02:20,808 --> 00:02:24,610
 I WANT TO BE THERE FOR STEVEN, 
      TO FIGHT BY HIS SIDE!     

57
00:02:24,612 --> 00:02:28,981
   THE EARTH IS MY HOME, TOO.   
    CAN'T I HELP PROTECT IT?    

58
00:02:28,983 --> 00:02:31,150
       O-OKAY.                  

59
00:02:31,152 --> 00:02:34,453
     IF THAT'S HOW YOU FEEL,    
     WE SHOULD GET STARTED.     

60
00:02:34,455 --> 00:02:36,288
                  WOO-HOO!      
                 [ LAUGHS ]     

61
00:02:36,290 --> 00:02:37,589
           WAIT, NOW?           

62
00:02:37,591 --> 00:02:38,991
        [ ENERGY BUZZES ]       

63
00:02:38,993 --> 00:02:41,493
             [ GRUNTS, LAUGHS ] 

64
00:02:41,495 --> 00:02:42,828
            YOU OKAY?           

65
00:02:42,830 --> 00:02:44,930
           IT CAN TAKE          
      SOME GETTING USED TO.     

66
00:02:44,932 --> 00:02:46,832
              WHOO! [ LAUGHS ]  

67
00:02:46,834 --> 00:02:49,601
    HEY, YOU TWO.               
      THIS WAY.                 

68
00:02:49,603 --> 00:02:51,336
                  RACE YOU.     

69
00:02:51,338 --> 00:02:52,804
          [ LAUGHTER ]          

70
00:02:52,806 --> 00:02:54,606
              WHOA.             

71
00:02:54,608 --> 00:02:57,009
THIS IS AN ANCIENT SKY ARENA,   
       CONNIE,                  

72
00:02:57,011 --> 00:03:00,012
 WHERE SOME OF THE FIRST BATTLES
      FOR EARTH TOOK PLACE.     

73
00:03:00,014 --> 00:03:02,548
           IT WAS HERE          
   THAT I BECAME FAMILIAR WITH  

74
00:03:02,550 --> 00:03:04,850
        THE HUMAN CONCEPT       
       OF BEING A KNIGHT,       

75
00:03:04,852 --> 00:03:08,520
COMPLETELY DEDICATED TO A PERSON
          AND A CAUSE.          

76
00:03:08,522 --> 00:03:11,623
  THIS IS WHAT YOU MUST BECOME, 
            CONNIE --           

77
00:03:11,625 --> 00:03:15,060
    BRAVE, SELFLESS, LOYAL --   
            A KNIGHT.           

78
00:03:15,062 --> 00:03:18,897
            WE BEGIN WITH A BOW.
      FIRST TO ME, YOUR TEACHER.

79
00:03:18,899 --> 00:03:21,533
                AND NOW AGAIN   
               TO YOUR LIEGE.   

80
00:03:21,535 --> 00:03:23,902
               OKAY. MY LIEGE.  

81
00:03:23,904 --> 00:03:25,637
    MISS KNIGHT.                

82
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:27,706
        [ BOTH CHUCKLE ]        

83
00:03:27,708 --> 00:03:30,475
               I HOPE YOU TWO   
      ARE TAKING THIS SERIOUSLY.

84
00:03:30,477 --> 00:03:32,544
           YES, MA'AM.          
MM-HMM. MM-HMM.                 

85
00:03:35,349 --> 00:03:37,316
                    COOL.       
               HOLOGRAM PEARL.  

86
00:03:37,318 --> 00:03:40,185
       TO BEGIN, THIS HOLO-PEARL
          WILL BE YOUR OPPONENT.

87
00:03:40,187 --> 00:03:42,821
LEVEL 0, BEGINNER SET.          

88
00:03:42,823 --> 00:03:45,357
DO YOU WISH TO ENGAGE           
     IN COMBAT?                 

89
00:03:45,359 --> 00:03:47,192
                    YES!        

90
00:03:47,194 --> 00:03:49,261
                   STEVEN?      
      HMM?                      

91
00:03:49,263 --> 00:03:50,996
         OH!                    
   UM, I'M SORRY.               

92
00:03:50,998 --> 00:03:53,232
SORRY, SORRY, SORRY, SORRY.     
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]          

93
00:03:53,234 --> 00:03:54,566
       REFLEX.                  

94
00:03:54,568 --> 00:03:58,170
UH, YOU JUST BE CAREFUL,        
AND I WILL GO OVER HERE.        

95
00:03:58,172 --> 00:04:01,773
    ALL RIGHT. EVERYTHING BEGINS
              WITH YOUR STANCE. 

96
00:04:01,775 --> 00:04:04,409
                 REMEMBER...    
           ♪ YOU DO IT FOR HIM ♪

97
00:04:04,411 --> 00:04:07,679
           ♪ AND YOU WOULD DO IT
                   AGAIN ♪      

98
00:04:07,681 --> 00:04:09,081
           ♪ YOU DO IT FOR HER ♪

99
00:04:09,083 --> 00:04:12,117
              ♪ THAT IS TO SAY  
          YOU'LL DO IT FOR HIM ♪

100
00:04:13,587 --> 00:04:16,455
       ♪ KEEP YOUR STANCE WIDE ♪

101
00:04:16,457 --> 00:04:18,590
♪ KEEP YOUR BODY LOWERED ♪      

102
00:04:18,592 --> 00:04:20,592
♪ AS YOU'RE MOVING FORWARD ♪    

103
00:04:20,594 --> 00:04:23,795
♪ BALANCE IS THE KEY ♪          

104
00:04:23,797 --> 00:04:26,265
♪ RIGHT FOOT, LEFT FOOT ♪       

105
00:04:26,267 --> 00:04:28,934
          ♪ NOW GO EVEN FASTER ♪

106
00:04:28,936 --> 00:04:30,869
               ♪ AND AS YOU'RE  
             MOVING BACKWARDS ♪ 

107
00:04:30,871 --> 00:04:33,572
        ♪ KEEP YOUR EYES ON ME ♪

108
00:04:33,574 --> 00:04:36,441
     ♪ KEEP MY STANCE WIDE ♪    
 GOOD.                          

109
00:04:36,443 --> 00:04:38,443
    ♪ KEEP MY BODY LOWERED ♪    
RIGHT.                          

110
00:04:38,445 --> 00:04:40,946
    ♪ AS I'M MOVING FORWARD ♪   

111
00:04:40,948 --> 00:04:42,381
    CONCENTRATE.                

112
00:04:42,383 --> 00:04:43,915
      DON'T YOU                 
  WANT HIM TO LIVE?             

113
00:04:43,917 --> 00:04:45,617
    ♪ RIGHT FOOT, LEFT FOOT ♪   

114
00:04:45,619 --> 00:04:48,153
YES, BUT PUT YOUR WHOLE BODY    
      INTO IT.                  

115
00:04:48,155 --> 00:04:51,123
♪ EVERYTHING YOU HAVE,          
EVERYTHING YOU ARE ♪            

116
00:04:51,125 --> 00:04:54,493
            ♪ YOU'VE GOT TO GIVE
            ON THE BATTLEFIELD ♪

117
00:04:54,495 --> 00:04:57,296
              ♪ WHEN EVERYTHING 
                 IS CHAOS ♪     

118
00:04:57,298 --> 00:04:59,831
          ♪ AND YOU HAVE NOTHING
          BUT THE WAY YOU FEEL ♪

119
00:04:59,833 --> 00:05:01,800
               ♪ YOUR STRATEGY  
                AND A SWORD ♪   

120
00:05:01,802 --> 00:05:04,503
          ♪ YOU JUST THINK ABOUT
          THE LIFE YOU'LL HAVE ♪

121
00:05:04,505 --> 00:05:07,105
      ♪ TOGETHER AFTER THE WAR ♪

122
00:05:07,107 --> 00:05:09,274
            ♪ AND THEN YOU DO IT
                  FOR HER ♪     

123
00:05:09,276 --> 00:05:11,643
           ♪ THAT'S HOW YOU KNOW
                YOU CAN WIN ♪   

124
00:05:11,645 --> 00:05:13,845
♪ YOU DO IT FOR HER ♪           

125
00:05:13,847 --> 00:05:18,483
  ♪ THAT IS TO SAY              
YOU'LL DO IT FOR HIM ♪          

126
00:05:18,485 --> 00:05:21,286
♪ DEEP DOWN YOU KNOW ♪          

127
00:05:21,288 --> 00:05:23,855
 ♪ YOU WEREN'T BUILT            
   FOR FIGHTING ♪               

128
00:05:23,857 --> 00:05:28,994
♪ BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN         
YOU'RE NOT PREPARED TO TRY ♪    

129
00:05:28,996 --> 00:05:30,996
♪ WHAT THEY DON'T KNOW ♪        

130
00:05:30,998 --> 00:05:33,965
♪ IS YOUR REAL ADVANTAGE ♪      

131
00:05:33,967 --> 00:05:38,970
♪ WHEN YOU LIVE FOR SOMEONE     
YOU'RE PREPARED TO DIE ♪        

132
00:05:38,972 --> 00:05:42,207
       ♪ DEEP DOWN, I KNOW      
     THAT I'M JUST A HUMAN ♪    

133
00:05:42,209 --> 00:05:43,775
        TRUE.                   

134
00:05:43,777 --> 00:05:45,711
♪ BUT I KNOW THAT I CAN ♪       
  ♪ BUT YOU KNOW THAT YOU CAN ♪ 

135
00:05:45,713 --> 00:05:48,880
♪ DRAW MY SWORD AND FIGHT ♪     
  ♪ DRAW YOUR SWORD AND FIGHT ♪ 

136
00:05:48,882 --> 00:05:51,316
♪ WITH MY SHORT EXISTENCE ♪     
              GOOD.             

137
00:05:51,318 --> 00:05:54,019
♪ I CAN MAKE A DIFFERENCE ♪     
         YES, EXCELLENT.        

138
00:05:54,021 --> 00:05:56,321
♪ I CAN BE THERE FOR HIM ♪      

139
00:05:56,323 --> 00:05:58,890
♪ I CAN BE HIS KNIGHT ♪         

140
00:05:59,893 --> 00:06:02,661
♪ I CAN DO IT FOR HIM ♪         

141
00:06:02,663 --> 00:06:04,363
      ♪ YOU DO IT FOR HER ♪     

142
00:06:04,365 --> 00:06:06,898
    ♪ OKAY, NOW,                
   DO THAT AGAIN ♪              
                     YES, MA'AM.

143
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:10,369
♪ YOU DO IT FOR HER,            
  AND NOW YOU SAY ♪             

144
00:06:10,371 --> 00:06:13,772
          ♪ I'LL DO IT FOR HIM ♪

145
00:06:18,212 --> 00:06:20,712
    CONNIE!                     
                HEY, STEVEN.    

146
00:06:20,714 --> 00:06:22,647
CONNIE, WAIT.                   
              HMM?              

147
00:06:22,649 --> 00:06:23,849
             AH, RIGHT ON TIME. 

148
00:06:23,851 --> 00:06:25,350
CAN WE TALK FOR A MOMENT?       

149
00:06:25,352 --> 00:06:26,752
        SURE. WHAT'S UP?        

150
00:06:26,754 --> 00:06:28,653
      WE HAVE IMPORTANT TRAINING
               TO DO, CONNIE.   

151
00:06:28,655 --> 00:06:29,888
           YES, MA'AM.          

152
00:06:29,890 --> 00:06:31,923
SHE'S BEEN MAKING GREAT STRIDES,
                   STEVEN.      

153
00:06:31,925 --> 00:06:34,559
               SHE'S GOING TO BE
               AN ASSET TO YOU. 
              HMPH.             

154
00:06:34,561 --> 00:06:36,161
        [ ENERGY BUZZES ]       

155
00:06:36,163 --> 00:06:37,396
            [ SIGHS ]           

156
00:06:37,398 --> 00:06:39,731
     [ LAUGHS ]                 
    WOW, GARNET.                

157
00:06:39,733 --> 00:06:41,933
THAT WAS THE FUNNIEST THING     
  I'VE EVER HEARD.              

158
00:06:41,935 --> 00:06:44,169
                   GARNET,      
              MASTER OF COMEDY. 

159
00:06:44,171 --> 00:06:45,904
           [ LAUGHS ]           
           YO, STEVEN.          

160
00:06:45,906 --> 00:06:48,907
   WHY ARE YOU STANDING THERE   
       ALL SAD LIKE THAT?!      

161
00:06:48,909 --> 00:06:51,576
W-WELL, CONNIE IS TAKING        
SWORD-FIGHTING LESSONS          

162
00:06:51,578 --> 00:06:52,878
     FROM PEARL.                

163
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:55,080
BUT I THINK IT'S GETTING        
A LITTLE TOO SERIOUS.           

164
00:06:55,082 --> 00:06:57,916
SHE WANTS CONNIE TO DO          
ALL THIS DANGEROUS STUFF FOR ME.

165
00:06:57,918 --> 00:06:59,584
              THAT MAKES SENSE. 

166
00:06:59,586 --> 00:07:01,720
  WHAT DO YOU MEAN?             

167
00:07:01,722 --> 00:07:03,422
      BACK DURING THE WAR,      
        PEARL TOOK PRIDE        

168
00:07:03,424 --> 00:07:05,857
   IN RISKING HER DESTRUCTION   
        FOR YOUR MOTHER.        

169
00:07:05,859 --> 00:07:08,260
       SHE PUT ROSE QUARTZ      
       OVER EVERYTHING --       

170
00:07:08,262 --> 00:07:13,198
  OVER LOGIC, OVER CONSEQUENCE, 
       OVER HER OWN LIFE.       

171
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:15,267
        HYAH!                   

172
00:07:15,269 --> 00:07:16,435
         YOU OKAY, DUDE?        

173
00:07:16,437 --> 00:07:18,136
I HAVE TO DO SOMETHING!         

174
00:07:18,138 --> 00:07:20,038
     THANKS FOR TELLING ME THAT!
                    BYE!        

175
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,441
      [ BREATHING HEAVILY ]     
               REMEMBER, CONNIE.

176
00:07:22,443 --> 00:07:25,610
          IN THE HEAT OF BATTLE,
         STEVEN IS WHAT MATTERS.

177
00:07:25,612 --> 00:07:27,412
              YOU DON'T MATTER. 

178
00:07:27,414 --> 00:07:29,881
         I DON'T MATTER.        
 HUH?                           

179
00:07:29,883 --> 00:07:33,985
             NOW, LET US BEGIN! 

180
00:07:36,957 --> 00:07:38,557
             CONNIE?            
 [ SWORDS CLANGING IN DISTANCE ]

181
00:07:38,559 --> 00:07:40,392
     CONNIE, WHERE ARE YOU?     

182
00:07:40,394 --> 00:07:42,160
    [ SHOUTING IN DISTANCE ]    

183
00:07:42,162 --> 00:07:45,464
             CONNIE!            

184
00:07:45,466 --> 00:07:46,932
     [ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]     

185
00:07:46,934 --> 00:07:50,268
   YOU WOULDN'T HAVE HAPPENED   
    TO SEE CONNIE, WOULD YOU?   

186
00:07:50,270 --> 00:07:53,738
UNREGISTERED COMBATANT          
      DETECTED.                 

187
00:07:54,942 --> 00:07:57,275
              [ GASPS ] CONNIE! 

188
00:07:57,277 --> 00:08:00,479
       STEVEN?                  
WHAT ARE YOU DOING OUT HERE?    

189
00:08:00,481 --> 00:08:04,182
        CONNIE, I DON'T WANT YOU
TO DO THIS ANYMORE -- NOT ALONE.

190
00:08:04,184 --> 00:08:06,985
     NO, STEVEN.                
  I UNDERSTAND NOW.             

191
00:08:06,987 --> 00:08:11,022
YOUR LEGACY, YOUR DESTINY --    
 YOU ARE EVERYTHING!            

192
00:08:11,024 --> 00:08:13,825
AND I -- I AM NOTHING.          

193
00:08:13,827 --> 00:08:17,696
BUT I CAN DO THIS FOR YOU.      
I CAN GIVE YOU MY SERVICE.      

194
00:08:17,698 --> 00:08:19,764
                     NO!        
            I DON'T WANT YOU TO.

195
00:08:19,766 --> 00:08:23,668
       STEVEN,                  
I'M DOING THIS FOR YOU!         

196
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,003
              HYAH!             

197
00:08:25,005 --> 00:08:28,039
        I NEED TO BE ABLE       
         TO PROTECT YOU.        

198
00:08:28,041 --> 00:08:30,275
BUT IF YOU'RE THE ONE           
   PROTECTING<i> ME,</i>               

199
00:08:30,277 --> 00:08:32,410
 THEN WHO'S THE ONE             
   PROTECTING<i> YOU?</i>              

200
00:08:35,282 --> 00:08:38,817
SOMEDAY SOON, WE MAY BE FIGHTING
           SOME REALLY BAD GUYS.

201
00:08:38,819 --> 00:08:43,955
 AND WHEN THAT DAY COMES, I WANT
    TO FIGHT WITH YOU, TOGETHER.

202
00:08:43,957 --> 00:08:48,093
           SO, PLEASE, WON'T YOU
         SHARE THIS JAM WITH ME?

203
00:08:54,368 --> 00:08:55,834
THIS IS MUCH EASIER.            

204
00:08:55,836 --> 00:08:57,369
              THAT'S THE IDEA.  

205
00:09:03,544 --> 00:09:07,045
           NO MATTER WHAT COMES,
            WE DO THIS TOGETHER!

206
00:09:07,047 --> 00:09:09,047
         Pearl: STEVEN!         

207
00:09:09,049 --> 00:09:12,817
    STEVEN, DON'T INTERFERE.    
SHE NEEDS TO TAKE ME ON HERSELF.

208
00:09:12,819 --> 00:09:14,553
             WHY? WE'RE A TEAM. 

209
00:09:14,555 --> 00:09:17,689
         SHE'S THE STRAWBERRY...
...AND HE'S THE BISCUIT!        

210
00:09:17,691 --> 00:09:21,326
        AND THAT MAKES US JAM...
BUDS!                           

211
00:09:21,328 --> 00:09:22,527
             WHA...?            

212
00:09:22,529 --> 00:09:25,130
        [ BOTH SHOUTING ]       

213
00:09:32,239 --> 00:09:34,239
            [ GASPS ]           

214
00:09:34,241 --> 00:09:35,941
                    HYAH!       

215
00:09:35,943 --> 00:09:38,510
     [ SHOUTS ]                 

216
00:09:38,512 --> 00:09:40,245
             ENOUGH!            

217
00:09:40,247 --> 00:09:42,747
